Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去为迎击大举进攻的数亿变动重力源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾留下了在太阳系外围使用黑洞兵器的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是如今的“黑洞Exelion”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即“宇宙怪兽”的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测在人类倾尽全力投入的反攻作战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由无人Buster Machine构成的\N太阳系绝对防卫系统被建造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:20.37,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时变动重力源的残存势力似乎幸存了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人类已经没有任何余力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会选择封印空间跳跃技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己封锁于太阳系之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防卫系统逐渐进化得更为强大、更有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其最终获得的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却极为讽刺的 与敌人变动重力源非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今被我们称之为“宇宙怪兽”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防卫系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:59.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,370)\c&H000000&\bord0}第3军司令官 德拉索提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了保护我们人类而建造的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾几何时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们似乎从自己应当保护的人类身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到了与敌人变动重力源相同的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.20,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星之推动者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚自治互助会的伙食究竟有多么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也该习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同伴们也全都在军方的管理下接受治疗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在设施内只要戴着矫正装置 就不会造成多大的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论Topless这种病有多么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦事件之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:51.48,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,370)\fad(500,0)}太阳系 新10号行星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们而言的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对真正的宇宙怪兽 变动重力源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量根本不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless已经不再是拯救人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless虽然是属于青少年特有的前额叶异常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要早期治疗 仍有希望重新融入社会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已着手订立药物与外科治疗的法令依据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已于前天发布毁弃条约事项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并完成对自治互助会的强制征收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来 即可着手准备与“宇宙怪兽”进行和谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎来了Buster Machine 7号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然能到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚才来探访 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说带一些姐姐喜欢吃的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会是身体检查 一会儿又是心理测验
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一直不肯放我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种边境 亏你能拿到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我开口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些特务大叔们就会想办法帮我找来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚吃的还是北京烤鸭和鹅肝酱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就算想去地球也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们说好了 要去姐姐的家乡找云雀对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只云雀可以给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是云雀 是鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主的手艺很差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球 送人这个就是希望对方能恢复健康
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该由探病的人来送才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顶安全帽很拉风嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得很开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…觉得很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在能力消失前就先提出丧失申请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没去确认能力是否消失 也就用不着绝望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 都是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我只是Buster Machine公社的承包维修工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着替它难过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手原本就是义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插在那里的那根角 年代更是久远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据公社的记录 那是500年前战斗时留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不将它修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf似乎不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦过脑干 整支贯穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为这样造成几个Exotic Maneuver无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一处理不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能会失去宝贵的战斗经验值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它代替了短暂的Topless 跨越时代累积经验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是人工智能的存在目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历任驾驶员的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部分属于六度修改之前的旧装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是40任之前的前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“十六夜 静默之夜独自上路”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“他停在原地 我离开此处”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是哪个时代 大家都只能注定单恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的只有战斗经验值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们则会被人遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他一直持续发着低烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过不可以随便进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我会好好反省的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说还是想请你教她折
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去一趟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是她的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕独自启程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要一份饯别礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意送我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要得到你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本身就是Buster Machine吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不就等于是永恒的Topless吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是充满自信又强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使明知你的温柔全是装出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还是那么喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不愿意看我一眼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我曾是Topless 所以才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都几岁的人了 什么Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么和果子系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什么姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.27,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,370)}旗舰 卡拉柯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最初观测到异状时的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边则是12分钟前的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为数惊人的“宇宙怪兽”开始集结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宇宙怪兽”的巢穴是人类从未涉足的神秘空域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是吸积盘内部 无法进行X射线和重力波探测
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:53.33,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【吸积盘】（Accretion Disk）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:53.33,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(35,35)}吸积物质在致密天体周围形成的盘状物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想确认内部的状况 只能派人直接进入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由与泰坦事件的相似性来推测…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的变动重力源将会再度入侵太阳系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会回来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺与我加入了准备前往“宇宙怪兽”巢穴的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都对诺诺寄予厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为Buster Machine7号会拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就不需要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.42,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系 原13号行星 雷王星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.52,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丧失9成的质量仅残留中心核 现在已非行星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不清楚原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星的鸟全都灭绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道火星上最后一只鸟的故事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从破壳而出的那刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就已经是最后一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从未曾飞上过天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直站在水边 从未尝试飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长大后的某个日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星群划过的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是要追逐流星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是飞往星星的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃了土生土长的火星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她最后的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于前方展开的“宇宙怪兽” 数量7万5千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在持续增加中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}8万5千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们真的不会攻击我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是守护巢穴的近卫部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}9万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}9万5千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是来迎接7号的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过10万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量如此庞大的“宇宙怪兽” 惟7号一人之命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅光景 就连身为Topless的你也会大为震惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是“宇宙怪兽”的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你随行是7号的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想展示你们之间力量的差异吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.97,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系 新11号行星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.30,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞 Exelion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.30,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,200)}＊前作中宇宙战舰Exelion在雷王星轨道引爆其内部坍缩炉所形成的黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宇宙怪兽”集中的能层边缘附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.57,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【能层】（ergosphere）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.57,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(35,35)}旋转黑洞的视界与无限红移面之间的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现逆向的重力变动值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其规模无法与泰坦事件相比拟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是变动重力源？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从黑洞里爬了出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从这个变动重力源被Exelion困住以来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宇宙怪兽”们一直持续致力将其封印住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正企图打破黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine7号前往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在用微型黑洞填补裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变周围的物理空间 形成坍缩炉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是现今已经失传了的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那神一般的力量能拯救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宇宙怪兽”的女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她根本就是太阳系的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7…号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下令舰队前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用重力{Gravitron}炮进行掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我们这支宇宙最强舰队与7号同进退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事物都不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非战斗员请离开舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员第一种战斗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备炮击进行重力消耗战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,76 78 80…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首重力炮 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将空间扭曲了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力变动值异常上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可视波长圈即将浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变动值的直径超过1万2千公里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1万2千公里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比地球还要大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尚未展露全体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7号发出光束攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连7号的光束都无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 请下令全员离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要尽速离开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令所有人员立刻离舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以容纳一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快 这是最后一艘逃生艇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉也变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎还有大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…在发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最早在火星上认识那时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宇宙怪兽”就一直在找诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们想要带回自己的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺好强 我跟她差得可远了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺一直很想变得跟姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都好羡慕姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和诺诺莉莉非常像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实诺诺莉莉并不特别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在颤抖？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是世界改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是诺诺改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起飞吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同本舰共残存12艘舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗舰识别信号消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宇宙怪兽”完全不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连7号也奈何不了它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 让舰队退下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来对付它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的Topless吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要投掷雷王星撞击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请退避到冲击波范围之外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是不可能办到那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和诺诺在一起 无论什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都办得到！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exotic Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless连星球都能推动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以秒速20公里直接撞击了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它并不是从Exelion黑洞里出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是吞噬了整个Exelion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够自由操纵黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使以雷王星撞击也不会死的人类天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.48,0:24:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测到以太分离波
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测变动重力源企图从本空域进行空间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.59,0:24:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离到达空间跳跃临界点还有300
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.13,0:25:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在无法解决它 人类会彻底灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.53,0:25:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将残存舰艇集合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.97,0:25:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要给它一击…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是白费力气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.48,0:25:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果是7号的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.45,0:25:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺 你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.69,0:25:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击倒它的机会只有它在进行空间跳跃前的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.59,0:25:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要比行星撞击更加强大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让7号进入雷王星残存的中心核
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.07,0:25:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以微型黑洞为导火线 诱发坍缩连锁反应
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.87,0:25:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让雷王星成为黑洞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种近距离的超重力崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.35,0:25:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该足以打倒变动重力源
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.55,0:26:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让她舍身作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.15,0:26:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我不会让诺诺一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.76,0:26:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.13,0:26:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.59,0:26:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人将要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.56,0:26:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起化作星辰吧 诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.28,0:26:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.92,0:26:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.30,0:26:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.53,0:26:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine7号拒绝出战逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.77,0:26:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然被她舍弃 就等于是丧失了防卫系统
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们只能靠自己的力量来对抗变动重力源了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.25,0:27:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.09,0:27:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人类要真正长大…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.53,0:27:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所必须经过的仪式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没想到她居然会临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离空间跳跃临界 1.5 1.2
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.14,0:27:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 变动重力源即将进行空间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.63,0:27:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.77,0:27:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺！
